Title: My first travel-Pilavakkal dam
DateModified: '2019-02-28'
DatePublished: '2019-02-28'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/my-first-travel-pilavakkal-dam
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: M.Selva  Kathrien
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "I went to pilavakkal dam with my friends and teacher.\n It situated in watrap,virudhunagar\
  \ district. Flower plants,water streams enhance beauty to dam.Large wooden swing\
  \ attached with metal chains.10 People can sit in the swing.\n I saw  seesaw and\
  \ I astonished.How is built?\n  I can't forget it.Precious moments in life,I travel\
  \ with my favorite teacher.She is kind.No worries. I am not ready to leave that\
  \ place.\n  I didn't take photographs.Fishing is not allowed.\n My parents told\
  \ me  \"Go to church every day\".\nI don't like to go to church every day.I attend\
  \ Sunday mass only.\n I want to stay in park until 6 p.m to avoid mass.Bad time\
  \ , I came to home before 6 p.m"
